profile_positions.description:
Member of Ricoh's senior management team, managing the legal teams, the legal and compliance affairs and strategic, operational and group related matters of the operating companies and newly acquired companies in a cluster of countries: 

2019-2023: Netherlands, Belgium, Luxembourg, Czech Republic and Slovakia and in additional responsible for looking after legal and contractual affairs of Ricoh EMEA's supply chain;

2021-2022: in addition to abovementioned cluster temporarily also managing the legal team and looking after legal affairs of Ricoh International and Ricoh's emerging markets group;

2023-present: Netherlands, Germany, Austria, Switzerland, Poland, Hungary, Czech Republic and Slovakia and in addition responsible for looking after legal and contractual affairs of Ricoh EMEA's supply chain.
